  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Uncover the wonders of the Italy’s lakes on this escorted tour. On this journey you’ll encounter some of the country’s most striking landscapes including its enchanting cities and crystal-clear lakes that marble the mountainous landscape. Not only will you see the famous three; </span><a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda" title="Lake Garda">Garda</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-maggiore" title="Lake Maggiore">Maggiore</a><span> and </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a466e45e88084c09a318aa7ecdfde7d4" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-como/como" title="Como">Como</a><span>, you’ll also have the chance to visit the smaller lesser known lakes of </span><a data-udi="umb://document/2e0965a933de4db38581b2be029f20d6" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-orta" title="Lake Orta">Orta</a><span> and Lugano. </span></p>
<div>
<p><strong>Maximum Group Size: </strong>26</p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/wonders-of-the-italian-lakes#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/wonders-of-the-italian-lakes#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/wonders-of-the-italian-lakes#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/wonders-of-the-italian-lakes#Hotels">Hotels</a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/wonders-of-the-italian-lakes#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
